<p id="newPost">This system is designed to retrieve a suggested keyword for your sentence.  Your total charachter length is not limited however for use in certain systems the charachter length may be limited. <span id="italicText">(Twitter for example limits the total post to 140 characters)</span></p><br><br>
<ol class="recent_posts">
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <li class="post">
  <p>
    <b>Thought:</b>
    <%= post.thought %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <b>Keyword:</b>
    <%= post.keyword %>
  </p>
  </li>
<%end%>
</ol>

<%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path,{:class=>"ui-button"} %>
